reviewText: Adding to collection, some duplicates, still glad to get them.

As a big fan of classic old westerns, I was delighted to come across this release from Legend Films. First, I have seen these films before and am already a fan. But it was a real treat to watch them in colorized versions. It really brings new life to these already wonderful westerns. Had to give this DVD set a 5 star rating--great for the western film lover in your life!!
